OL,3,C'Miss appointment twice and you'll go
OL,4,Cto the back of the queue', says Miles
OL,6,FJeremy Miles MS wants to see 200,000
OL,7,Fpeople off waiting lists and numbers
OL,8,Fback to pre-pandemic levels by next
OL,9,FMarch.
OL,11,FAlongside that, the Welsh Government
OL,12,Fsays it is working with health boards
OL,13,Fto restore the eight-week target for
OL,14,Fdiagnostic testing to ensure no-one
OL,15,Fwaits more than two years for planned
OL,16,Ftreatment.
OL,18,FFrom June, the NHS Wales App will also
OL,19,Fbe updated to allow people to track
OL,20,Ftheir place on the waiting list.
