OL,3,C'Miss appointment twice and you'll go
OL,4,Cto the back of the queue', says Miles
OL,6,F"These missed appointments delay care
OL,7,Ffor everyone and waste valuable
OL,8,Fresources that could be helping other
OL,9,Fpeople.
OL,11,F"Evidence shows people who are in
OL,12,Fbetter health recover from surgery
OL,13,Ffaster, have fewer complications and
OL,14,Frequire shorter hospital stays.
OL,16,F"By ensuring people are properly
OL,17,Fprepared and fully informed about
OL,18,Ftheir treatment options, we can
OL,19,Fachieve better outcomes while making
OL,20,Fmore efficient use of NHS resources."
