OL,3,C'Miss appointment twice and you'll go
OL,4,Cto the back of the queue', says Miles
OL,6,F"The Welsh Labour Government want to
OL,7,Fplace more accountability on the
OL,8,Fpatient yet they've cut preventative
OL,9,Fhealth funding and have failed to turn
OL,10,Fthe dial on moving towards a more
OL,11,Fpreventative agenda for the long term.
OL,13,F"Instead, what we are hearing are
OL,14,Ffurther plans to increase the use of
OL,15,Fthe private sector at the expense of
OL,16,Finvesting in preventative measures
OL,17,Fwithin the NHS, such as increased
OL,18,FAllied Health Professionals.
