OL,6,F"This government has consistently
OL,7,Fblamed patients, health managers and
OL,8,FRoyal Colleges for various problems,
OL,9,Fwithout once taking responsibility for
OL,10,Ftheir failures.
OL,12,FResponding to proposals by Wales'
OL,13,Fhealth secretary Jeremy Miles to
