OL,3,C'Miss appointment twice and you'll go
OL,4,Cto the back of the queue', says Miles
OL,6,F"Plaid Cymru has a plan to tackle NHS
OL,7,Fwaiting lists. Earlier this year we
OL,8,Fannounced actions that a Plaid Cymru
OL,9,Fgovernment would take on day one,
OL,10,Fincluding establishing a new executive
OL,11,Ftriage system; strengthening
OL,12,Fcollaboration between health boards to
OL,13,Fidentify spare capacity; embracing
OL,14,Ftelemedicine to speed up assessments;
OL,15,Fmatching staffing levels to demand in
OL,16,Fkey specialities; and creating
OL,17,Ftemporary surgical hubs across Wales
OL,18,Fto get people treated faster.
