OL,3,C'Miss appointment twice and you'll go
OL,4,Cto the back of the queue', says Miles
OL,6,F"Wales - and the NHS - needs a fresh
OL,7,Fstart. No more sticking plaster
OL,8,Fsolutions or short-term thinking. Only
OL,9,FPlaid Cymru has the energy, the ideas
OL,10,Fand the plans, developed in tandem
OL,11,Fwith clinicians and health experts, to
OL,12,Fdeliver the change our health service
OL,13,Fso desperately needs."
